blog.title: Sorry Baby
blog.description: Ash / 18 / lesbian / I yell about tv shows a lot

body:
**Killing Eve spoilers**

You’ve been warned! I’m going to talk about the books.

So, in the preview for next episode you can hear konstantin say “you have to kill her” to villanelle. By the way she reacts it’s pretty obvious he’s talking about Eve. I think this is a sign that they are about to team up. Towards the end of the second book villanelle is tasked with killing eve, and instead of doing that she shows up to Eve’s house and tells her the situation. She believes that after she kills eve, the 12 might also kill her because she was “compromised” by the situation. She decides to protect Eve and fakes Eve’s death before they run away together. While I don’t think it’ll happen exactly like that in the show I do think it’s definitely going to be the thing that makes her switch sides in order to protect Eve.

So basically we’re all about to lose our shit after the next episode
